{"id": 5349, "title": "Ticket #5349: HTCondor RPMs should not \"provide\" .so files in private directories", "description": "<blockquote>\nWe package our own \"external\" libraries and they are stored in a directory that only HTCondor consults. However, rpmbuild automatically scans the entire install tree for shared object and puts them in a \"Provides\" section. We need to filter out the scanning of the private directories (especially for the condor-externals RPM) and put in explicit dependencies in the other RPMs.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2015-Nov-12 11:46:10 by tim:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>CODE REVIEW:</strong> Looks good, Carl</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Nov-16 17:18</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/72d57d41fef924d20eb6fcb56eb1480e2cb26f86\">[46268]</a></span>: Add version history for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5349\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5349'); return false;\" title='HTCondor RPMs should not \"provide\" .so files in private directories'>#5349</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5382\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5382'); return false;\" title=\"Restart from checkpoint failing for HTCondor 8.4.1\">#5382</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"defer\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5383\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5383'); return false;\" title=\"The %cmake macro includes extra undesired CFLAGS for RPM builds\">#5383</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wi